#about.text-center
  %h3 CCC Video Operation Center
  %img{ src: 'img/30c3katze-nibbler.jpg', alt: '30C3 - Winkekatze' }

  #container
    #content
      CCC Video Operation Center (C3VOC) is a working group consisting of
      %a{ href: 'https://ccc.de' } Chaos Computer Club
      enthusiasts running lecture recording and streaming infrastructure on and for different chaos
      %a{ href: 'https://c3voc.de/eventkalender'} events or conferences
      \.
      #sections
        #content-events
          .logo
            %a{ href: '#events' }
              %i.fa.fa-4x.fa-video-camera
          .headline
            %h4 Events
          .content
            We try to cover all events organized by the CCC and close friends.
        #content-contact
          .logo
            %a{ href: '#contact' }
              %i.fa.fa-4x.fa-envelope
          .headline
            %h4 Contact
          .content
            Leave a comment, yell at us or just chat
        #content-recordings
          .logo
            %a{ href: 'http://media.ccc.de' }
              %i.fa.fa-4x.fa-cloud
          .headline
            %h4 Recordings
          .content
            Bridge the time gap between events and have a look into the video archive

        #content-streaming
          .logo
            %a{ href: 'http://streaming.media.ccc.de' }
              %i.fa.fa-4x.fa-play-circle-o
          .headline
            %h4 Streaming
          .content
            We're doing it live!1!!

#events.text-center
  = render '_events'
  %a{ href: "#top", class:"back-to-top" } Back to Top



#contact.text-center
  %h3 Contact
  %img{ src: 'img/raw_IMG_7044_klein.jpg' }

  #container
    #content
      .text
        The most direct way to reach us is to visit us on
        %a{href: 'irc://irc.hackint.org:9999/#voc-lounge'} irc.hackint.eu
        in #voc-lounge .
        %br
        You can also reach us via email
        %a{href: 'https://spamty.eu/mail/v4/771/vFMIbqGt5l8abffaf9/', onclick: "window.open(this.href, '', 'toolbar=0,scrollbars=0,location=0,statusbar=0,menubar=0,resizable=0,width=820,height=700'); return false;", title: 'Reveal this e-mail address' } v...@c3voc.de
        \.
        %br
        We try to document most of the setup in the public pages of our
        %a{href: 'https://c3voc.de/wiki', target: '_blank'} wiki
        %br
        Stay up to date by following us on Mastodon, Twitter or even GitHub if you are interested in looking behind the scene.
